===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|synamome}}, from {{der|en|fro|cinnamone}}, from {{der|en|la|cinnamon}}, {{m|la|cinnamōmum}}, from {{der|en|grc|κιννάμωμον}}, later {{m|grc|κίνναμον}}, probably to be explained as “Chinese [[amomum]]”, {{m|grc|ἄμωμον}} being, only cognate to {{cog|syc|ܚܡܵܡܵܐ|tr=ḥəmāmā}} and {{cog|ar|حَمَامَا}}, a [[phytonym]] of lost [[provenience]] for a [[w:List of Amomum species|varied]] genus ''[[Amomum]]'' of spice and drug plants; compare for this composition the Iranian designation {{m|fa|دارچین|tr=dârčin|lit=Chinese tree}}.

